main.welcome-title: Welcome to Finotex's online processing system!
main.welcome-description-p-1: This site was built with our customers in mind as a means to process your orders efficiently and keeping you informed through our automatic system.
main.welcome-description-p-2: If you already have your log-in information,
main.welcome-description-p-3: please select the log in link located on the left side bar of this page in order to begin.
main.welcome-description-p-4: If you don't have a username or password and you would like to request one, please e-mail us at website@finotex.com.
main.welcome-description-p-5: Please note this site is only for existing customers that have already been set-up in our FOPS system.
main.welcome-description-p-6: We hope we help minimize time and energy in your ordering process, Should you have any suggestions or comments about our site. please e-mail us at marketing@finotex.com
main.request-detail: Through here, you’ll be able to file a complaint, claim, return or congratulate regarding the services we offer.
main.chatbot-detail: Through here, you can make inquiries to our chatbot.
main.footer-main-description: WE PROVIDE BRAND IDENTITY FOR TOP APPAREL COMPANIES WORLDWIDE. FIND OUT HOW FINEOTEX CAN IMPROVE YOUR BRAND'S IMAGE
main.info-pqrs-description: We strive to constantly improve the quality of our services and our relationship with our Finotex customers, as well as serve them with the excellence they deserve. Through here, you can fill a complaint, claim, return, or congratulate regarding our services. In order to get started, please file a new request.
main.info-pqrs-complain-description: A disagreement, dissatisfaction or discontent that a client may present when receiving inadequate attention from the company.
main.info-pqrs-claim-description: A demand made by a user because no service was provided or it was done poorly.
main.info-pqrs-return-description: A requirement made by a user to return a product purchased due to non-conformities with it.
main.info-pqrs-congratulation-description: User Satisfaction regarding the Entity, its services or servers.
